cast.overview: A New York stockbroker refuses to cooperate in a large securities fraud case involving corruption on Wall Street, corporate banking world and mob infiltration. Based on Jordan Belfort's autobiography.
cast.title: The Wolf of Wall Street

details.biography: Michael Izquierdo is an American actor and producer, known for "Succession" (2018), "The Wolf of Wall Street" (2013) and 11.22.63 (2016). He has an MFA from New York University's Tisch’s Graduate Acting Program. Izquierdo is the founder of Sunnyside Films.
details.name: Michael Izquierdo
details.place_of_birth: New York, New York, United States
